# TicketScout — Cloudflare Pages URL routing
# Routes clean SEO URLs to the appropriate template pages.
# :splat captures the wildcard portion and passes it as ?slug=
# so the template can read it via URLSearchParams.

# Concert/artist pages
/concert/:slug    /concert.html?slug=:slug    200

